news.title: Airport Authority officials to inspect land for second airport in Bengaluru
news.para: The Karnataka State Industrial and Infrastructure Development Corporation (KSIIDC) managing director Khushboo Goel Chowdhary briefed the AAI team about the proposed three places identified by the govt for setting up the airport.

news.title: Mumbai: BMC set to launch e-marketplace for TDR this week
news.para: The BMC has created the TDR marketplace on a SAAS platform. All Development Rights Certificates (DRC) will be dematerialised and maintained in an electronic format.

news.title: Lukewarm response to KHB’s project in Mysuru
news.para: As per the proposal, the board wanted to build 160 2 BHK apartments and 32 three BHK apartments. Rs 49.4 lakh was fixed as the provisional rate for two BHK apartments, while Rs 63 lakh was fixed for three BHK apartments.
